 brands and products include tootsie rolls and tootsie pops frooties fruit flavored chewy candy childs play assorted candies dots gumdrops and crows licorice candy andes chocolate mints charms blow pops and caramel apple pops sugar daddy and sugar babies caramels charleston chew candy bars junior mints cellas chocolatecovered cherries fluffy stuff cotton candy dubble bubble razzles and cry baby chewing gum niklnip juice confection wax lips flavored wax candy bonomos turkish taffy polar mint referencesedit  a b alison griswold  january  tootsie roll ceo dies at  we may never know how many licks slate magazine   a b kesling ben august   tootsies secret empire the wall street journal pp b–b   a b c andrew f smith  encyclopedia of junk food and fast food greenwood publishing group isbn   entry tootsie roll p   ellen rubin gordon  interview on abctv world news now reading  letter from clara tootsie hirshfield written when she was  years old  schlesinger hank  melvin gordon is dead at  led tootsie roll industries vending times retrieved    watt abigail  ceo and chairman of tootsie roll melvin gordon dies at  candy industry retrieved    strom stephanie  melvin j gordon who ran tootsie roll industries dies at  new york times retrieved    tootsie roll candies  cambridge brands cambridge ma  iconic factories on waymarkingcom  external linksedit tootsie roll industries web site tootsies secret empire a ceo in his s helms an attractive takeover target so whats next no one really knows wall street journal profile v t e confectionery products of tootsie roll industries andes chocolate mints caramel apple pops cellas charleston chew charms blow pops childs play crows cry baby dots dubble bubble fluffy stuff frooties wackowax lips junior mints niklnip razzles sugar daddy sugar babies tootsie rolls tootsie pops retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitletootsierollindustriesoldid categories confectionery companies of the united statestootsie roll industries brandsmanufacturing 